puts "In a decade with two leap years, like the decade from 2000 to 2010, there are " + ((365*24*60*8) + (366*24*60*2)).to_s + " minutes in this decade."
puts "\nKeep in mind, in a decade with 3 leap years, like from 1999 to 2009, the number of minutes is " + ((365*24*60*7) + (366*24*60*3)).to_s + "."
